Well, we had Burmese ayahs - but that\rquote s not a Burmese word - but it meant a nanny, otherwise all the house servants were not Burmese, they were mostly Indian \endash  Hindus.  But they were very sweet, I think.  And that\rquote s the level 
of memories, of being in a park together with other children - and photographs.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 And then after that? 

