\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Mary:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Yes. (LAUGHS)  Is this
 important for you?  He was a very a literary person, and he made us read all his childhood books, so again, we read }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Captains Courageous}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 , and all the Henty books, and all the W.W. Jacob books.  As we grew older, we read all the books he liked as a boy.  Bu
t he also liked to talk about Horace, and Greek and Latin, and he was organising plays for the Drama Society, which he actually founded in Marlow, Bucks., so that we read all the one-act plays he could [find] in the house, and then he loved, at table, he 
loved to discuss origins of words.  (LAUGHS)  My sister was very left out, always two years behind, you see!  So he gave me - and also good writing and bad writing.  And he was always writing for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Punch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 , or about fishing.  He was publishing little essays, an
d I have about 25 of them, about fishing.  And my dearest wish is to get them published, as a collection.  They\rquote ve all been published once, but I want to write something about him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 
So perhaps your rather clear way of writing is partly due to his influence.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Mary:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 I\rquote 
m sure he would have been very strict with me, yes.  Yes.  My husband is a bit strict too!
