\rquote  intentions for their marriages.  And then he wrote a very important piece on famine for them.  But the general idea, and also his earlier work on kinds of markets, which he was
 very pleased with, I felt it was too facile really.  He found markets working, and he identified markets, but he fought a losing war whic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid12063999 
h he created between so-called \lquote formalists\rquote  and the \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 substantivists}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
