\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Mary:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 
Hard.  I often think about it.  Hard.  Very complex.  Very merc
urial, and difficult to pin down.  With his students, formal.  With people he despised, very rude, and he despised a lot of people.  And with his friends, very charming and warm and kind.  What else?  Funny, he wanted to be funny a lot.  He wanted to make
 jokes.
