\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Yes, rather!  Srinivas was more a close friend than Steiner.  He died recently.  He didn\rquote 
t know any French, and so he felt very disadvantaged, that he couldn\rquote t read Marcel Mauss, who hadn\rquote t been translated.  It was probably due to his problems.  E-P started this whole translation of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 L'Ann\'e9e Sociologique}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 
