\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6650702\charrsid6650702 Yeah.  Love to!  If that\rquote s enough about Srinivas, I was going tell you about how I was afraid.  He went to India and left us, and he said, 
\'93I haven\rquote t got any lodgings for when I come back.  I have to give up my lodgings, so could you find me some?\'94  So I put an advertisement, he said, \'93Could you put an advertisement in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
