m going to say something more about his real respect, his real religion.  His religion was personal.  And so he told me about somebody who lit a candle, which is an act of piety, in his 
opinion, though they wanted it for the smell, and then snuffed it out, he said, \'93How could you do that?  Something offered to a god, and you\rquote ve snuffed it out like that!\'94  So he was always looking out for these sensitive\'85  Okay.  So that
