h indeterminacy, some things can\rquote t be classified by their system, and they have an option of either enlarging their system.  I now realise that that\rquote 
s what the lady did, because they had a classification of animal life, which was environmental, so that they had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10897844 animals as the above \endash  the sky;}{
